<%- include('partials/header') %>

<div class="container">
    <header>
        <h1>PROFITEERS PMC</h1>
        <div class="subtitle">The Largest LGBTQ+ Arma 3 Unit</div>
        <div class="tagline">Freedom. Discovery. Fat Stacks of Cash.</div>
    </header>

    <section class="section text-center">
        <img src="/ressources/intro-pic.png" alt="Hero image of breaker" style="margin: 20px auto; width: 50vw; max-width: 100%; min-width: 80%;" class="image-placeholder"/>
        <div style="font-size: 1.15em; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 30px;">
            Profiteers PMC is an LGBTQ+ friendly, inclusive, semi-serious unit set in a modern conflict-driven world. 
            Governments are collapsing, riots shake entire nations, and private military companies rise to fill the void. 
            <br><br>
            <strong style="color: var(--accent);">Will you answer the call?</strong>
        </div>
        <a href="https://discord.gg/profiteers" class="btn btn-primary">Join Discord Now</a>
    </section>

    <div class="grid grid-3">
        <div class="card text-center">
            <div style="font-size: 2em; margin-bottom: 10px;">📅</div>
            <h3>Operations</h3>
            <p style="color: var(--accent); font-size: 1.2em; font-weight: 700;">Saturdays</p>
            <p>17:00-20:00 UTC<br>11:00-14:00 EST</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card text-center">
            <div style="font-size: 2em; margin-bottom: 10px;">🌈</div>
            <h3>Inclusive</h3>
            <p>LGBTQ+ friendly community where everyone is welcome and no discrimination is done</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card text-center">
            <div style="font-size: 2em; margin-bottom: 10px;">🎮</div>
            <h3>Semi-Serious</h3>
            <p>Serious enough to succeed, fun enough to enjoy</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <section class="section">
        <h2>OPERATIONS</h2>
        <img src="/ressources/ops.png" alt="Profiteers during operations" style="margin: 20px auto; width: 100%;" class="image-placeholder"/>
        <p>
            Missions range from small skirmishes to full-on brutal front line warfare. 
            All operations are created and provided by our Zeus team and Operations Department. 
            We're always looking for more people to create unique stories.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
        <h2>CULTURE</h2>
        <img src="/ressources/culture.jpg" alt="Profiteers during operations" style="margin: 20px auto; width: 100%;" class="image-placeholder"/>
        <div class="grid grid-2">
            <div>
                <h3>In-Game</h3>
                <p>We take operations seriously enough to succeed, without demanding perfection. Focus on teamwork and having a good time.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3>Out-of-Game</h3>
                <p>We're a laid-back community of friends. Many of us are LGBTQ+, and we don't tolerate anyone looking to punch down.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3>Immersion</h3>
                <p>Our campaigns are shaped by custom lore written by multiple community members, woven directly into our missions.</p>
            </div>
            <!-- <div>
                <h3>Structure</h3>
                <p>We don't use ranking systems. <strong style="color: var(--accent);">Everyone plays on equal footing.</strong></p>
            </div> -->
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section text-center">
        <h2>Ready to Join?</h2>
        <p style="font-size: 1.2em; margin: 20px 0;">
            No mandatory attendance. Just show up and have fun.
        </p>
        <a href="/join" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
        <a href="https://discord.gg/profiteers" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-left: 15px;">Join Discord</a>
    </section>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
